  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best tools to create video infographics with?",
  "response": "There are several excellent tools available for creating video infographics, each with its own unique features and capabilities. Here are some of the best options:\n\n1. **Adobe After Effects**:\n   - A powerful tool for animation and visual effects.\n   - Offers a high degree of customization and professionalism.\n   - Supports plugins and templates for easier creation.\n\n2. **Animaker**:\n   - User-friendly platform specifically designed for creating animations and infographics.\n   - Provides templates and a drag-and-drop interface.\n   - Includes various characters, props, and backgrounds to use.\n\n3. **Canva**:\n   - While primarily a graphic design tool, Canva also has video creation capabilities.\n   - Offers a range of templates and easy drag-and-drop functionality.\n   - Great for beginners and includes many stock images and video clips.\n\n4. **Veed.io**:\n   - An online video editing platform that includes tools for creating infographics and animations.\n   - Features templates, subtitles, and other editing capabilities.\n   - User-friendly interface for quick and easy editing.\n\n5. **Piktochart**:\n   - Primarily known for creating infographics, but also allows for animated presentations and videos.\n   - Easy to use with a variety of templates for different purposes.\n   - Good for visual storytelling.\n\n6. **Powtoon**:\n   - Focuses on creating animated videos and presentations.\n   - Offers many templates geared toward infographics.\n   - Easy to use, making it suitable for beginners.\n\n7. **Visme**:\n   - A versatile tool for creating presentations, infographics, and videos.\n   - Provides templates and a user-friendly interface.\n   - Includes features for animations and interactive content.\n\n8. **Moovly**:\n   - Provides a platform for creating animated videos and infographics.\n   - Offers a library of assets, including images, sounds, and animations.\n   - Suitable for both beginners and more experienced users.\n\n9. **Biteable**:\n   - An online video maker with templates for different styles, including infographics.\n   - Simple drag-and-drop interface.\n   - Good for creating social media videos quickly.\n\n10. **Renderforest**:\n    - An online video and animation maker offering templates for infographics.\n    - Allows easy customization and export options.\n    - Suitable for marketing videos and presentations.\n\nWhen selecting a tool, consider your specific needs, such as ease of use, available templates, customization options, and budget. Most of these tools offer free trials or free versions, so you can explore and find the one that suits you best.",
